text: Saheed Akorede Okunola (born 1969), popularly known as Saheed Osupa or King Saheed Osupa is a Nigerian musician, performer and film actor. His genre of music is majorly fuji. ==Biography== Saheed Osupa was born in Ibadan, Oyo State but grew up in Lagos State where he completed his early education. In 1983, Saheed Osupa chose music as his profession and went on to release his first record album titled Fuji Fa Disco which earned him fame. He has released over 25 record albums. == Related pages == * List of Nigerians == References == Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian musicians Category:Singers Category:People from Lagos State
